Matchstick Hummingbird 

Presenting the 1st piece of an 22 piece two part series titled: 11/11 Soul, Mind, Body & Personality 

The series showcases the 22 domains of the human experience in conservation with the soul.  Outlining universally shared experiences that translate the collective consciousness and misunderstandings of the human experience. A brilliant and digestible blueprint for navigating a world of seemingly enormous flaws yet total perfection. 

Matchstick Hummingbird 

The Hummingbird is a most powerful totem that holds enormous influence in our perspective of how big or small we are in the universe.  As the smallest bird on the planet it exhibits unique and tenacious traits that now other animal is capable of on the planet. The matchstick is a direct reflection of the original source of energy, fire, and the will of such a determined creature to spark inspiration by embodying and trusting the four domains of our existence which are the soul, mind, body and personality. 

The Universally shared experience that the hummingbird puts all beings through is as follows: Every human being’s trust was violated at some point by somebody who said they were going to love them and protect them, even if it was a perceived violation.  Since said violation the architecture of how they process energy and information is restructured, knowingly and unknowingly. 
 

The message of the Hummingbird is to always set your intention, take action and then trust that the Soul, Mind and Body are operating as an equal three way team to guide the Personality in the direction of their highest potential and the greatest vision for their life.  If you question yourself and your everyday experience in life it becomes the ultimate violation of trust by not allowing these three entities to do their job. Let’s the Soul, Mind and Body be 33% partners and the personality gets to exist in its beautiful 1% lane and not suffer but assuming it knows better than the almighty trinity of this three gifts.

It’s the “I” and the “We” the soul, mind and body. It’s a collective effort to ride the wave, now let go and hang ten. 🤙🏼

Dear Today, From Tomorrow 

If you’re reading this, it’s Today 
A message from tomorrow
I thank you in advance 
for this time i must borrow 

Whether you’re happy or sad, 
Celebrating or in Sorrow 
This message, i beg 
it’s important; from Tomorrow 

Don’t make yourself small,
just because others aren’t big
it’s irrelevant 
when there’s one life that is lived 

You’re calling, it’s calling! 
it holds a delicate time 
You’ll know 
Dear, Hermes 
I’ll send you the sign 

Don’t let your wings go to fast for your feet 
I promise my friend 
when it’s time 
at the runway they will meet 

Love your life 
to the highest and largest 
you’re enormous
in every dimension
This… I promise 

Be gentle, yet firm with yourself 
and with
 your precious health 

I thank you from down the road 
for trusting your luck 
good & bad 
you never got stuck 

you grew 
and you never died 
so please my dear friend
slow down 
BIGGER STRIDES! 

You got this 
I love you
i’ll see you down the road 
if you’re reading this message 
it’s today 
from tomorrow

Thomas Lampshire
